{
  "info": {
    "name": "Go Gin Agent — Orquestador Multi-Agéntico",
    "description": "Colección completa para el orquestador multi-agéntico Go + Gin.\n\n## Setup\n1. Configura las variables `base_url`, `jwt_secret` y `jwt_refresh_secret`\n2. Ejecuta **Register** (necesitas una invitación previa en la DB)\n3. Ejecuta **Login** — los tokens se guardan automáticamente\n4. Las demás requests usan el token automáticamente\n\n## Auto-refresh\nEl access token se inyecta en todas las requests protegidas vía la variable `{{access_token}}`.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "base_url",
      "value": "http://localhost:8080",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "access_token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "refresh_token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      {
        "key": "token",
        "value": "{{access_token}}",
        "type": "string"
      }
    ]
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "🏥 Health",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Health Check",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/health",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["health"]
            },
            "description": "Verifica el estado del servidor: SQLite, memoria, goroutines, uptime."
          },
          "response": [],
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Database connected', function () {",
                  "    var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(json.database).to.eql('connected');",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Security headers present', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.header('X-Content-Type-Options');",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.header('X-Frame-Options');",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.header('X-Request-ID');",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "🔐 Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register",
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "noauth"
            },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"admin@acme-corp.com\",\n  \"password\": \"SecureP@ss123\",\n  \"name\": \"Admin User\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/register",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "register"]
            },
            "description": "Registra un nuevo usuario. **Requiere invitación previa** en la DB.\n\nPassword: mínimo 8 chars, 1 mayúscula, 1 número, 1 símbolo."
          },
          "response": [],
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 201 Created', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(201);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('User created', function () {",
                  "    var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(json.message).to.eql('account created successfully');",
                  "    pm.expect(json.user).to.have.property('id');",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "noauth"
            },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"admin@acme-corp.com\",\n  \"password\": \"SecureP@ss123\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "login"]
            },
            "description": "Autentica un usuario y devuelve access_token (15min) + refresh_token (7d).\n\nLos tokens se guardan automáticamente en las variables de la colección."
          },
          "response": [],
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Tokens received', function () {",
                  "    var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(json).to.have.property('access_token');",
                  "    pm.expect(json).to.have.property('refresh_token');",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "// Auto-save tokens to collection variables",
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('access_token', json.access_token);",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('refresh_token', json.refresh_token);",
                  "    console.log('✅ Tokens saved to collection variables');",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Login (Invalid Password)",
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "noauth"
            },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"admin@acme-corp.com\",\n  \"password\": \"wrongpassword\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "login"]
            },
            "description": "Test de login con credenciales inválidas. Debe devolver 401 con mensaje genérico (sin revelar si el email existe)."
          },
          "response": [],
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 401 Unauthorized', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(401);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Generic error message', function () {",
                  "    var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(json.error).to.eql('invalid credentials');",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Refresh Token",
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "noauth"
            },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"refresh_token\": \"{{refresh_token}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/refresh",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "refresh"]
            },
            "description": "Rota el refresh token: revoca el anterior y genera un nuevo par access + refresh."
          },
          "response": [],
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "// Auto-save new tokens",
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('access_token', json.access_token);",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('refresh_token', json.refresh_token);",
                  "    console.log('✅ Tokens rotated and saved');",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
